{"tid":2204957,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[慷他人之慨]賑災基金撥款助孟加拉水災災民","createTime":"2020-09-16T12:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T12:26:41.000Z","uid":48149,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"956af41c0c9f62ea005bb121b2f427bf92474d85","tid":2204957,"uid":48149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:13:42.000Z","msg":"政府從賑災基金批出682.7萬元予兩間機構，賑濟孟加拉水災災民。<br />\n <br />\n撥款中，297.2萬元批予香港世界宣明會，385.5萬元撥給香港仁人家園，約63,750名災民受惠。<br />\n <br />\n兩間救援機構賑災的地點不同，沒有資源重疊。機構完成賑災計劃後，須向賑災基金諮詢委員會呈交評估報告和經審核的帳目，確保撥款用於指定用途。<br />\n<br />\n2020年9月16日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/09/20200916/20200916_184403_251.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020%2F09%2F20200916%2F20200916_184403_251.html&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvT8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=3a886cce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/09/20200916/20200916_184403_251.html</a>"},{"pid":"1194e389d1ae1219edce0cb7ffdc07ac4367b6a0","tid":2204957,"uid":3167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:17:35.000Z","msg":"自己地方民生都唔掂仲衝去救災<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38704037cd2888458d3912f2129c4f8dd7f6f69c","tid":2204957,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:19:55.000Z","msg":"唔反對<br />\n孟加拉無所謂<br />\n<br />\n強国實屌爆佢"},{"pid":"4d7a605d9fbaa84104cb0d7cf76d0913a1efc510","tid":2204957,"uid":317305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c062bb61d00de96fc202d44f06ece0d2cd924e00","tid":2204957,"uid":48149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:22:58.000Z","msg":"拎香港人血汗錢幫支那做統戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb5fd6af0ef826a7c68deede805a1bc1793a6db","tid":2204957,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"強